Package: click
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Modular router.
 Click is a tool for building flexible and configurable routers.
 .
 A click router is assembled from simple elements that implement simple functions,
 such as packets classification, queuing, scheduling and interfacing with network devices.
 A click configuration is a graph of elements that send each others packets and process them.
 .
 This package provides the userspace tools for using click.
